d of the company\u2019s financial standing Perform audits to ensure accounting department is compliant with company policies Controller requirements This section should list the essential qualities of an ideal candidate. Include previous work experience, education or achievements that would be beneficial. And list any preferred hard and soft skills. Example Controller requirements Must be a Certified Public Accountant Minimum of 10 years experience in accounting roles Detailed oriented and analytical mindset Previous experience in a management or leadership role Knowledge of local, state and federal financial laws and regulations Excellent communication skills and a collaborative mindset Controller related job titles: Business Controller Financial Controller Division Finance Manager Finance Manager Divisional Controller Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
